/* Accessibility/Keyboard Messages */
"Turn on Vibe Coding Guard in System Settings ▸ Accessibility, then come back." = "在系統設定 ▸ 輔助功能中開啟 Vibe Coding Guard，然後返回這裡。";
"macOS will ask for permission once so the keyboard can be locked." = "macOS 會要求一次權限，以便鎖定鍵盤。";
"When you turn Keep Awake off, the keyboard unlocks automatically." = "當您關閉防睡眠時，鍵盤將自動解鎖。";
"Turn this on if a pet or kid might step on the keyboard while a job runs." = "如果寵物或小孩可能在工作執行時踩到鍵盤，請開啟此選項。";

